{"tid":1110361,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)完全猛鬼手册 重案夢幻組 蝙蝠俠2","createTime":"2019-04-16T13:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T19:21:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98566a416c8021f5912844fdb077b7cf5647ac00","tid":1110361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=bdb2469a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2b8d0b03\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=46b6109e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-67dUcIM01j4/TML3uY33rNI/AAAAAAAAET4/RPw0Ntl2SFw/s1600/In+the+Mouth+of+Madness.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-67dUcIM01j4%2FTML3uY33rNI%2FAAAAAAAAET4%2FRPw0Ntl2SFw%2Fs1600%2FIn%2Bthe%2BMouth%2Bof%2BMadness.jpg&h=3fe66814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d0/Bad_boys_two.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd0%2FBad_boys_two.jpg&h=d5347368&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://tinomelvan.files.wordpress.com/2014/04/batmangame.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinomelvan.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F04%2Fbatmangame.jpg&h=ab83c13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.劇情是說約翰［John Trent］是名優秀的保險調查員兼自由作家，受出版社雇用調查知名恐怖小說家賽特凱恩［Sutter Cane］神秘失蹤的案件。凱恩的恐怖小說似乎具有能影響讀者的神秘魔力，甚至讓人做出瘋狂行為。約翰從賽特凱恩的小說中發現某些線索，可能指向凱恩躲藏的地點，於是他與女編輯琳達［Linda Styles］一同動身前往。向來鐵齒的約翰發現隨著路途他似乎與現實越來越遙遠，一步步進入了凱恩創造的惡夢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.在第一部電影之後8年，警探麥克&middot;勞里（Mike Lowrey，威爾&middot;史密斯飾演）和馬奎斯&middot;巴涅特（Marcus Burnett，馬丁&middot;勞倫斯飾演）正在追查進入邁阿密的迷幻藥源頭。他們追蹤著幾隻來自古巴，來到一個三K黨聚會，毒品也在這裡進行交易。在交火中，麥克意外射傷了馬奎斯的臀部，使得馬奎斯開始考慮自己是否想要和麥克繼續搭檔.........<br />\n<br />\n3.高譚市一群黑社會份子計劃行劫銀行並在行動中互相殘殺，餘下的最後一人在槍傷銀行經理後揭開了面罩：小丑（Joker）。同時蝙蝠俠和詹姆斯&middot;戈頓（James Gordon）決定讓檢察官哈維&middot;丹特（Harvey Dent）加入打擊市內犯罪勢力。雖然兒時好友兼戀人瑞秋（Rachel Dawes）與哈維展開了約會，布魯斯&middot;韋恩（Bruce Wayne）認同後者打擊罪犯的決心因而為他舉行籌款。<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=58630b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ee5a712b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09373ca44ccb27c35fa26df918a94470734981bf","tid":1110361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058de752c2a65eef4d557a1bf3d2d963394f7b4f","tid":1110361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa71993b3cc1a35166fa3343d7ff53a8d556484","tid":1110361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6115489529976d03d8835aadcdba527e9e21dfe0","tid":1110361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}